message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted to exceed expectations. This exceptional item boasts a range of features that cater to the most discerning needs, making it a true standout in its category. Given its quality and craftsmanship, I believe it's worth more than $150 to you. Would you consider purchasing it for $200? I'm confident it will be a valuable addition to your collection.
